# Doom Runner

## Tests

Run `npm test`

## Start Test Server

Build agent first `npm run build`

Run `npm run server`

Test are located in the `test-example` folder

## Init tests

You need to get the server to look for tests open http://localhost:7777/init and it will do this.

## Connect agent

Open http://localhost:7777/agent

You can open as many agents as you like. It should make the test run go faster.

Once a test run is complete you can open the init page again to start over

## View results

Open http://localhost:7777/results
